videos.headline: Campbell takes early lead with 18-yard TD
videos.description: Daniel Smith connects with Caleb Snead to give the Fighting Camels a 7-0 lead over the Coastal Carolina Chanticleers.

videos.headline: Anderson threads the needle for Coastal Carolina TD
videos.description: Kilton Anderson shows poise and finds Malcolm Williams for a 12-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Campbell QB Smith dives into the end zone for 14-yard TD
videos.description: Daniel Smith gets flushed out of the pocket and runs down the sideline for a 14-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Williams hauls in TD for Coastal Carolina
videos.description: Kilton Anderson throws a 38-yard touchdown pass to Malcolm Williams for Coastal Carolina's first lead of the game.

videos.headline: Coastal Carolina extends lead with 30-yard rushing TD
videos.description: Torrance Marable finds room on the outside and scores from 30 yards out.
